------ Test: map option outer reference
Select1: x => (case when !(some(x) == None) then some((some(x).get < x)) else None)
------ end

------ Test: map seq outer reference
Select1: x => fromRepr(seq(x, x + 1).map(x1 => (x1 < x)))
------ end

------ Test: read
ReadPath: path=/tmp/test, format=Parquet, unpivot=false, filenameGlobFilter=*
------ end

------ Test: read+filter
Filter: x => (x < 10)
    ReadPath: path=/tmp/test, format=Parquet, unpivot=false, filenameGlobFilter=*
------ end

------ Test: read+selectN+filter+join
Join: (l, r) => (l._1 == r._1)
    SelectN: x => x, x => (x == 1)
        ReadPath: path=/tmp/test, format=Parquet, unpivot=false, filenameGlobFilter=*
    Filter: x => (x._2 < 1)
        ReadPath: path=/tmp/right, format=Parquet, unpivot=false, filenameGlobFilter=*
------ end

------ Test: ternary
Select1: x => (case when (x < 10) then x else 0)
------ end
